        <fields>
            <name>Body</name>
            <fieldText>&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;Whether you&apos;re a Full Time Employee or a Contractor, all Ohana@Home Remote employee badge requests will need to be completed using the following article:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;u&gt;Badge Photo Criteria&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Employee must be standing in front of a SOLID WHITE background.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Photo must be well-lit. No shadows over the face. (Use flash)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Employeesâ€™ entire head and shoulders must be in frame.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;No scanned copies of photos will be accepted.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;No hats or headwear, unless worn for religious purposes.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;No sunglasses.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Eyes must be open.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Photos must be high resolution.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Photos must be in focus.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Employee must be looking directly into the camera.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;No black and white photos. Photos must be color.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;No effects of filters are allowed on photos.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Photo must be in either *.JPG or *.PNG format&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;When you have your picture ready return to this onboarding task and click Next to request your badge.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;For more information about terms and conditions of use, please refer to concierge&lt;/p&gt;</fieldText>
            <fieldType>DisplayText</fieldType>
        </fields>
        <showFooter>true</showFooter>
